Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,————————————————————- ＯＰ————————————————————\N-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:34.73,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果てしない空をゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.83,0:01:38.12,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見えない翼が導く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.23,0:01:40.14,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥か彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:46.88,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}僕らを待つ　まだ見ぬ未来へと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:56.54,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Always　覚め切ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.71,0:01:59.54,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速すぎるthat night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.74,0:02:06.28,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透明な闇に囲まれ　誰も似た輪の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.38,0:02:09.35,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Find you　あの日の風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.47,0:02:12.68,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揺れ動いた場所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:14.01,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eternal my pass
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.06,0:02:18.96,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全て君に合うためのプロセスだったね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.35,0:02:22.05,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly opened my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.11,0:02:24.48,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need the brightness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.96,0:02:28.42,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼方から聞こえる予感に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.47,0:02:32.52,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓動を震わせていたいから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:36.31,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a reality　It's a reality
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.37,0:02:39.79,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can believe myself for again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:43.19,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光の中 目覚めていく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:46.85,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じてくれた君となら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:48.05,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:49.29,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never lost my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:52.67,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ここで生まれ変わる景色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:56.25,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷さえ今　誇りになる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.29,0:03:00.86,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}だから君とBurst The Gravity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:34.73,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沒有盡頭的天空中行走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.83,0:01:38.12,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由看不見的羽翼引導
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.23,0:01:40.14,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通向遙遠的比方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:46.88,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,300)}那看不見的未來依舊在等待我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:56.54,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Always 不願清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.71,0:01:59.54,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了 that night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.74,0:02:06.28,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被那透明的黑暗包圍 誰也逃不出這個圈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.38,0:02:09.35,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Find you 那日的風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.47,0:02:12.68,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變幻不定的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:14.01,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eternal my pass
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.06,0:02:18.96,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都是為了與你相會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.35,0:02:22.05,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly opened my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.11,0:02:24.48,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need the brightness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.96,0:02:28.42,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自彼方聽聞的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.47,0:02:32.52,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令我震動鼓舞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:36.31,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a reality　It's a reality
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.37,0:02:39.79,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can believe myself for again
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:43.19,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在光的沐浴下 我漸漸清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:46.85,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是你 我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:48.05,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:49.29,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never lost my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:52.67,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏不斷變化的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:56.25,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的傷口 是我的驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.29,0:03:00.86,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}因為你和Burst The Gravity
